Restaurants and online food delivery platforms generate large amounts of order data, but they often struggle to understand customer ordering behavior, popular food items, peak ordering times, and sales trends.
This lack of insight makes it difficult to improve customer satisfaction, optimize menu offerings, and increase revenue.
The objective of this project is to analyze food ordering data using Tableau to identify customer preferences, ordering patterns, and key business trends, enabling data-driven decision-making.

Objectives of the Project
--------------------------------
- Analyze customer ordering behavior.
- Identify the most popular food items.
- Find peak ordering days and times.
- Study sales trends and customer spending.
- Create interactive Tableau dashboards to support business decisions.
